headline: Newmont: Gold's All-Time High Helps, But Costs In Focus Ahead Of Earnings
summary: Newmont's Q3 2024 results missed expectations. VanEck Gold Miners ETF outperformed the S&P 500 since early 2024. Read why I maintain a buy rating on NEM stock.

headline: Newmont: 2025 Comeback Story Is Showing Promise
summary: NEM's valuation isn't expensive, but production integration risks and cost inflation risks have hampered optimism, leading to relative underperformance. Read more here.
